title: STARKVietnam Conference 2022 | Vietnam's First StarkNet Conference
short_desc:
STARKVietnam is a developer-oriented conference presented by Topology to help grow the StarkNet ecosystem in Vietnam and greater South East Asia. STARKVietnam is the first StarkNet conference in South East Asia and is honored to kickstart the movement in Vietnam for the first time. The conference is filled with exciting workshops to learn about Cairo and StarkNet.

Pioneers of the StarkNet ecosystem will be there to share their experiences with ambitious builders from the region.
